HEADWORD: dignitary
<hw>dig"ni*ta*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>dignitaries</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[Cf. F.
